    Short ribs ground round beef swine tri-tip cupim shank picanha biltong bresaola shoulder fatback tail pork loin. Kielbasa prosciutto cupim sirloin pancetta.
  </p><p>Pork chop beef ribs frankfurter chicken spare ribs, drumstick biltong short loin porchetta pastrami tri-tip flank.</p> -->
</div>

<style define:vars={{ imgUrl }}>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .item {
    border: 1px solid #333;
    height: auto;
    width: 100vw;
    text-align: center;
    /* color: var(--textColor); */
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    background: hsl(60, 60%, 61%);
    background-image: var(--imgUrl);

    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
  }
  .item:not(:first-of-type) {
    opacity: 0.4;
    transition: opacity 2s;
  }
  .item.fade-in {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    width: 90vw;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
</style>
<style is:global>
  p.transform {
    /* background-color: red; */
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  p {
    transform: translateY(50px);
    transition: transform 1s;
  }
</style>
